review_comments.body:
Can you reflow these comments to be a little more descriptive, like this:

``` C++
if (year % 4 != 0) {
    // Not divisible by 4, so not a leap year.
   return false;
} else if (year % 100 != 0) {
    // Divisible by 4, but not by 100, so it is a leap year.
    return true;
} ...
```

